Package popt4jlib.TS

Tabu Search with Short-Term Memory Structure Parallel Implementation.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DblArray1CMaker
    implements the operator for creating random chromosome objects that are of type double[] for the Tabu-Search meta-heuristic.
    DblArray1MoveMaker
    specifies how to make a move from one position to the next, when "positions" are double[] objects for the Tabu-Search meta-heuristic.
    DTS
    The DTS class implements a parallel Tabu Search algorithm for the minimization of a function to be passed in as argument object implementing the FunctionIntf argument of the minimize(f) method.
    DTSIndividual
    auxiliary class, not part of the public API.
    DTSThread
    auxiliary class not part of the public API.
    DTSThreadAux
    auxiliary class not part of the public API.
    UpdateTLTask
    auxiliary class not part of the public API.
